Problem Statement :
Given a string S consisting of upper/lower-case alphabets and empty space characters ‘ ‘. 
The string may contain spaces at the end. You will have return the length of last word which consists of alphabets only.
Input:
S = "Geeks for Geeks"
Output: 5
Explanation: The last word is "Geeks" of length 5.

Problem Statement Link :
https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/problems/length-of-last-word5721/1?page=1&category=Strings&difficulty=Basic,Easy&sortBy=submissions

Solution :
class Solution 
{ 
    int findLength(String s) 
    { 
        String arr[] = s.split("\\s");
        return (arr[arr.length - 1].length());
    }
}
